				</button>
				<div class="top-separator"></div>
				<div id="top-title"><span class="top-dot"></span><b>Lv 的电脑</b></div>
				<span class="beta-badge">β 开发中</span>
				<div class="top-marquee">INTERNET ANGEL SYSTEM // ZUREEALLV.COM</div>
				<a class="back-blog" href="/">返回旧博客</a>
				<time id="clock">00:00:00</time>
			</header>

			<nav id="desktop-icons" aria-label="应用程序">
				<button data-open="stream"><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/icons/youtube.png" alt="" /><span>直播</span></button>
				<button data-open="games"><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/icons/game.png" alt="" /><span>游戏</span></button>
				<button data-open="archive"><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/icons/clock.png" alt="" /><span>闹钟</span></button>
				<button data-open="health"><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/icons/medications.png" alt="" /><span>Health Care</span></button>
				<button data-open="links"><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/icons/map.png" alt="" /><span>地图</span></button>
				<button data-open="internet"><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/icons/internet.png" alt="" /><span>互联网</span></button>
				<button data-open="jine"><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/icons/jine.png" alt="" /><span>JINE</span><i class="badge">3</i></button>
			</nav>

			<aside id="angel-status">
				<div class="status-title">INTERNET ANGEL</div>
				<div class="status-grid">
					<span><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/status/icon_status_follower.png" alt="" />FOLLOWER <b>4,700</b></span>
					<span><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/status/icon_status_love.png" alt="" />LOVE <b>88</b></span>
					<span><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/status/icon_status_stress.png" alt="" />STRESS <b>31</b></span>
					<span><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/status/icon_status_yami.png" alt="" />DARKNESS <b>66</b></span>
				</div>
			</aside>

			<section id="window-layer"></section>

			<section id="start-menu" hidden>
				<div class="start-brand">
					<img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/icons/kangel.png" alt="" />
					<div><b>Lv</b><small>INTERNET ANGEL USER</small></div>
				</div>
				<div class="start-body">
					<button data-open="computer"><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/icons/folder_open.png" alt="" /><span><b>我的电脑</b><small>所有内容与文件夹</small></span></button>
					<button data-open="internet"><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/icons/internet.png" alt="" /><span><b>互联网</b><small>浏览 zureeallv.com</small></span></button>
					<button data-open="jine"><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/icons/jine.png" alt="" /><span><b>JINE</b><small>消息与留言板</small></span></button>
					<button data-open="about"><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/icons/ame.png" alt="" /><span><b>关于 Lv</b><small>USER PROFILE</small></span></button>
					<a class="start-home-link" href="/">↩ 返回现在的博客</a>
				</div>
				<footer>† 愿互联网天使保佑你 †</footer>
			</section>

			<nav id="dock" aria-label="快捷启动">
				<button data-open="computer" title="我的电脑"><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/icons/folder_open.png" alt="" /></button>
				<button data-open="status" title="状态"><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/icons/heart.png" alt="" /></button>
				<button data-open="notes" title="便签"><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/icons/text.png" alt="" /></button>
				<button data-open="gallery" title="相册"><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/icons/folder_photos.png" alt="" /></button>
				<button data-open="internet" title="互联网"><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/icons/internet.png" alt="" /></button>
				<button data-open="stream" title="直播"><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/icons/youtube.png" alt="" /></button>
			</nav>

			<template id="window-template">
				<article class="window">
					<header class="titlebar">
						<span class="title-square"></span>
						<b class="window-title"></b>
						<div class="window-controls">
							<button data-action="minimize" aria-label="最小化">_</button>
							<button data-action="maximize" aria-label="最大化">□</button>
							<button data-action="close" aria-label="关闭">×</button>
						</div>
					</header>
					<div class="window-content"></div>
					<footer class="window-grip"><i></i><i></i><i></i></footer>
				</article>
			</template>

			<div id="notification"><img src="/lab/internet-angel/assets/icons/kangel.png" alt="" /><span></span></div>
			<div class="crt"></div>
		</main>
		<script is:inline id="angel-posts" type="application/json" set:html={postsJson}></script>
		<script is:inline src="/lab/internet-angel/app.js"></script>
	</body>
</html>
